        },
        "description": "Estimated in-flight requests via Little's Law: rate(started[1m]) × mean duration. Mean derived from the histogram's _sum / _count so the long-tail :slow flavour is reflected. Approximate — derived from counters because no true concurrency gauge is emitted yet.",
